# Testing

- Use the Vitest workspace projects from `vitest.workspace.ts`; project names are `alchemy/<package>`.
- Reuse shared `.vitest` setup for `~test`, global setup, timeouts, and local chain fixtures.
- Chain/bundler tests may need Foundry/Anvil, Rundler, and `VITEST_SEPOLIA_FORK_URL`.
- Prefer `./scripts/run-affected-tests.sh v5.x.x` for branch-level package validation.
- Read `.agents/skills/testing/` before changing test setup or fixture behavior.
